{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4f67a79e6c","title":"敬告士兵群众书","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"726a000a59","index":0,"year":1929,"month":3,"day":27,"articleId":"4f67a79e6c"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji4-1","name":"毛泽东全集第4卷(1)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji4-1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji4-1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"5d90fc9005","type":"paragraph","text":"敬告士兵群众书！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"4f67a79e6c"},{"id":"af688e7072","type":"paragraph","text":"（1929年3月27日）","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"4f67a79e6c"},{"id":"65e1b7ef07","type":"paragraph","text":"本军是共产党的军队，是贫苦工农的化身，我们替为工农利益奋斗，以求得到彻底的解放！","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"4f67a79e6c"},{"id":"923a7e42d6","type":"paragraph","text":"你们与工农同是被压追的贫苦群众，国民党、军阀、豪绅地主是你们共同的敌人，为解放工农，为解放你们自己，我们特地号召你们起来：实行兵变！回枪打张贞叫！回枪杀压追你们的长官！参加土地革命、分取土地！","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"4f67a79e6c"},{"id":"fab6b2ba98","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]这是毛泽东和朱德向国民党暂编第一师发布的《敬告士兵群众书》的主要内容。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"4f67a79e6c"}],"page":{"id":"32009ef67b","publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"4f67a79e6c","start":222,"end":222}}}},"__N_SSG":true}